watch
Discworld Player Help
watch

.SH Name
.SI 5
watch - make an effort to become more alert to your surroundings
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
watch
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Watch makes you temporarily more alert to your surroundings, giving
you an improved perception for a while.  It costs 50 other guild
points and the duration, and improvement, are dependent on your
(prior) bonus for other.perception.  You will also stop watching
your surroundings if they change, that is, if you move or are moved.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> watch
You force yourself to be more alert and to watch your surroundings
more intently.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
look
.EP
